    "body": "This PR has https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/14376 as a prerequisite; changes to spack core will be merged in that one and then I'll rebase this branch.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n- Add a new package VecCore as a Spack-based dependency rather than having VecGeom's cmake auto-download and install\r\n- Prevent auto-downloading of unused test data during VecGeom installation\r\n- Use target microarchitecture instead of variant to determine instruction set\r\n- Add shared library and CUDA support to VecGeom\r\n- Add GDML and ROOT support to VecGeom\r\n- Update a ROOT dependency (Davix) because of a version compatibility issue declared by ROOT",
